activity.title: openfoodfacts/openfoodfacts-server#11853
activity.text:
Thanks for your additions. Good you found this entry. Not sure why it is still in ingredients at all. Any ingredient that is the result of processing (usually with a processing adjective) should not be there.

Have a look at ingredients_processing.txt(?). There you will find purée (any translations missing?) as well. If so the ingredient can be deleted.

This approach implies that we do not have to add to many translations.
